## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```bash

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/barber-shop-landing.git

2.	Navigate to the project directory:

cd barber-shop-landing

3.	Open the index.html file in your browser to view the landing page.

**Usage**

Simply open the landing page in a browser, and the page will adapt to the deviceâ€™s screen size. Users can interact with the booking form to schedule an appointment.

